<p><strong><a title="srubdoma" href="../local/img/98b9559c0488dc198f6eff8e84868722.jpg"><img style="margin: 5px 20px; float: left;" src="../local/img/.thumbs/98b9559c0488dc198f6eff8e84868722_320_0_0.jpg" alt="srubdoma" width="169" height="119" /></a></strong><span style="font-size: large;"><strong>Срубы </strong></span></p>
